NewsDay has received images of a reckless Toyota Mark X driver who crashed into a home in Kuwadzana Extension injuring a three year old girl who was playing in the yard on Monday morning. The impact shown by eye-witness images show that the driver was speeding when he lost control of the steering wheel. Below are pictures of the accident: <img src="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1.jpg" alt="" width="1080" height="608" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3096224744037289" srcset="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1.jpg 1080w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1-30x17.jpg 30w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /> <img src="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2.jpg" alt="" width="1080" height="608" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3096224744037290" srcset="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2.jpg 1080w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2-30x17.jpg 30w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /> <img src="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3.jpg" alt="" width="1080" height="608" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3096224744037291" srcset="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3.jpg 1080w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/3-30x17.jpg 30